Aku kagum.

57
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,840
Tuan Murong,

58
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,280
jujur saja.

59
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,320
Aku hanya pejabat daerah,

60
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,200
