89
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,480
Tangkap dia!

90
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,680
Menolak penangkapan,

91
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,640
menghalangi tugas resmi,

92
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,680
