93
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,720
Siapa yang berani?

94
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,160
Maju!

95
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,760
- Mengmeng!
- Jangan bergerak!

96
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,880
Letakkan senjata!

97
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,000
Jika tak ingin dia mati
di hadapan kalian,

98
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,840
